        <h3><a href="../comment/8708#comment-8708" class="permalink" rel="bookmark">What locale do you use?</a></h3>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Zemalf, what locale is in use on your system? I don't use Windows, so won't be able to try to debug your problem, but I'm guessing it's due to the system language settings on your system that you need to add the code you mention. Localization is still a black-box mystery for me, I'm afraid :-(</p>
<p>Thanks for your comment, and pardon me for the delayed response - I've now subscribed to the comments RSS feed, in Google Reader. Hopefully that will update me when a new comment is posted.</p>
<p>Regards,<br />
Ed.</p>
